# Google Apps Script Rules

Write Apps Script in modular files:
- config.gs
- ids.gs
- signup.gs
- training.gs
- entry.gs
- judging.gs
- finalists.gs
- certificates.gs
- emailTemplates.gs

Every automation should:
1. Validate required fields
2. Avoid duplicate processing
3. Log email sends
4. Catch errors
5. Write errors to an Email Log or Error Log tab

Use clear constants for sheet names and column headers.
Avoid hard-coded column numbers when possible.
Prefer header-based lookup.
